overview: He knew his partner was down for some hard work when he saw his bright pink shirt and that hungry look in his pants.  When the big boss pulled over his underling to get a special report, the underling showed he knew how to carry his weight.  The lazy guy in the office thinks he can get away with anything, but his colleagues are going to put him through the ringer.  It's a high pressure business that leaves some men whimpering in the dust, but not these two big players.  There's no better way to let off some steam at the end of the day then by getting a good feel for your co-worker's assets.
title: Office Twinks 5
